{"tid":955284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【年尾流流】龍岩巴士遭劫持撞人群釀5死21傷　1人被捕　","createTime":"2018-12-25T09:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T10:51:56.000Z","uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"afbcf9e35ebe8dcd1b90198367580148c47a2b62","tid":955284,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"龍岩巴士遭劫持撞人群釀5死21傷　1人被捕　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181225/mobile/bkn-20181225171003441-1225_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181225%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181225171003441-1225_00952_001.html&d=%2Bx%2FO5aMVOz%2Fb6Hk2i1FBcwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3c0cff5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181225/mobile/bkn-20181225171003441-1225_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n福建龍岩一部巴士周二（25日）下午傳被人挾持後再撞向人群，造成多人死傷。當地警方表示，目前已拘捕1名疑犯；但並未證實事件是否涉及有人挾持巴士，以及造成多人傷亡。"},{"pid":"577d00d6e7bb561517a23c5f311c2c8e773cbe41","tid":955284,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181225/photo/bkn-20181225171003441-1225_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181225171655\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181225%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181225171003441-1225_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181225171655&h=02d3d6b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"919ced444ab843f47b7f89b3d2b8acb0c5030b91","tid":955284,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"等睇老貓gif"},{"pid":"2876fe35e768bef12efc5ee487903944a40c6f6b","tid":955284,"uid":29982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:35:58.000Z","msg":"勇武派"},{"pid":"4ecd87a8b9c6b7e1969fc97b2465f0d0e45686ec","tid":955284,"uid":66514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"唔想知呀.jpg"},{"pid":"3cce4442ddc464452754ea981ba6ffa00561d646","tid":955284,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6c024d81499105e23dad890323a772ec16f63f","tid":955284,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"治癒"},{"pid":"6f84205ffb985fcbe9444224312da7dedc9260ed","tid":955284,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b0f71876a44a40efb6c4bba0eff07a33405176","tid":955284,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:17:15.000Z","msg":"睇錯龍運巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7d9ca0d04e44223ed5f6cca3269a9fda2ddd19","tid":955284,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:18:42.000Z","msg":"cctvb唔撚報"},{"pid":"5b1cea8442dceef720c945dacb9ab8ab2d9f4eed","tid":955284,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181225/large/1545729888_04c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181225%2Flarge%2F1545729888_04c2.jpg&h=84e5cf3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b18d354e0bd1d646fcbd3e16581107e62b6fe8f4","tid":955284,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"【血腥聖誕】福建男脅持巴士撞人群滿地傷者 至少5死21傷<br />\n<br />\n（更新內容、新增影片）聖誕節傳來悲劇！今日福建省龍岩市一名男子，據悉因不滿政府遷拆，報復社會，脅持一架35號巴士並胡亂撞向街道途人，造成至少5死21傷，死者包括一名警員。福建省龍岩市公安局指出，目前疑兇已被捕。<br />\n<br />\n根據微信「西湖業主內務群組」截圖顯示，事發在蓮東市場的土樓坪巴士站。從網傳影片可見，一架巴士的樓梯級上被濺上血紅鮮血，有電單車被捲落車底，多輛汽車被撞毀。<br />\n<br />\n網上消息指，涉案男子是新陂村民，因為政府遷拆，對社會不滿，殺了一名村幹部及警員。當地居民則指，35號巴士是龍岩市很重要的巴士線，經過全市主要醫院、商業街、體育中心、市政府及學校。<br />\n<br />\n當地黨委、政府正在全力救助傷者，疑兇在事發後在現場被捕，案件正在調查中。《新京報》報道，下午4時40分左右，龍岩急救部門稱，傷者被送往龍岩市第一醫院、龍岩市第二醫院和龍岩市人民醫院救治，其中傷重者被送到龍岩市第一醫院。龍岩市人民醫院工作人員稱，該院接收了約6、7人，其中有人昏迷。"}]}